-- Anadarko May Buy 75 Percent Stake in Onshore Jolly Ranch, Independent Says
-- Catherine Airlie
-- 2010-07-25T12:25:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/anadarko-may-buy-75-percent-stake-in-onshore-jolly-ranch-independent-says.html

          
          
             Anadarko Petroleum Corp.  may buy a
75 percent stake in the onshore Jolly Ranch project in Colorado,
the  Independent on Sunday  reported, without saying where it got
the information.  
 The stake in the project, a 50:50 joint-venture between
Running Foxes Petroleum Inc. and  Nighthawk Energy Plc , may cost
between $300 million and $1.5 billion, the newspaper said.  
